org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.api

Interface AggregationQueryBuilder<P extends Persistable,R,T,A extends AggregationQueryBuilder<P,R,T,A>>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - input type for the aggregation
    R - result type for the aggregation
    T - data type of the entries for the aggregation
    A - the type of the builder, useful for extending this builder and maintaining the builder type
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseQueryBuilder<R,AggregationQuery<P,R,T>,A>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    VectorAggregationQueryBuilder<P,R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregationQueryBuilderImpl, VectorAggregationQueryBuilderImpl

    public interface AggregationQueryBuilder<P extends Persistable,R,T,A extends AggregationQueryBuilder<P,R,T,A>>
extends BaseQueryBuilder<R,AggregationQuery<P,R,T>,A>
    This and its extensions should be used to create an AggregationQuery.
